sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant MW as Main Window
    participant SD as SwiftData Store
    participant MB as Menu Bar
    participant HK as Hotkey Launcher
    participant CB as Clipboard

    U->>MW: Create or edit prompt
    MW->>SD: Debounced save (updatedAt)

    U->>MB: Open menu bar
    MB->>SD: Query prompts

    U->>HK: Press ⌘⇧P
    HK->>SD: Query prompts

    U->>HK: Copy or paste action
    HK->>CB: Write clipboard (sets lastUsedAt)
    CB-->>U: Clipboard available
